Carmen Serano https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carmen_Serano 0 Carmen Serano (born Carmen Maria Robles; August 18, 1973) is an American actress. She starred in the 2007 film Urban Justice alongside Steven Seagal. She is most notable for her role as Assistant Principal Carmen Molina in the television series Breaking Bad.
